{"id": "test-03400", "text": "The result leaves Real on 38 points after 16 games, four ahead of Barcelona.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 18, "end": 22, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "Real"}, {"start": 66, "end": 75, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "Barcelona"}]}
{"id": "test-03401", "text": "With just one league match scheduled before the New Year break, Real are also assured of spending Christmas ahead of their arch-rivals.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 64, "end": 68, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "Real"}]}
{"id": "test-03402", "text": "A mix-up in the Barcelona defence let Croatian international Suker in midway through the first half, and Montenegrin striker Mijatovic made it 2-0 after fine work by Clarence Seedorf just after the break.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 16, "end": 25, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "Barcelona"}, {"start": 38, "end": 46, "ent_type": "MISC", "text": "Croatian"}, {"start": 61, "end": 66, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Suker"}, {"start": 105, "end": 116, "ent_type": "MISC", "text": "Montenegrin"}, {"start": 125, "end": 134, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Mijatovic"}, {"start": 166, "end": 182, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Clarence Seedorf"}]}
{"id": "test-03403", "text": "Barcelona fought back strongly but were twice denied by the woodwork on an unusually quiet night for Brazilian striker Ronaldo.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 9, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "Barcelona"}, {"start": 101, "end": 110, "ent_type": "MISC", "text": "Brazilian"}, {"start": 119, "end": 126, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Ronaldo"}]}
{"id": "test-03404", "text": "SOCCER - PSV HIT VOLENDAM FOR SIX.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 9, "end": 12, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "PSV"}, {"start": 17, "end": 25, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "VOLENDAM"}]}
{"id": "test-03405", "text": "AMSTERDAM 1996-12-07", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 9, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "AMSTERDAM"}]}
{"id": "test-03406", "text": "Brazilian striker Marcelo and Yugoslav midfielder Zeljko Petrovic each scored twice as Dutch first division leaders PSV Eindhoven romped to a 6-0 win over Volendam on Saturday.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 9, "ent_type": "MISC", "text": "Brazilian"}, {"start": 18, "end": 25, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Marcelo"}, {"start": 30, "end": 38, "ent_type": "MISC", "text": "Yugoslav"}, {"start": 50, "end": 65, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Zeljko Petrovic"}, {"start": 87, "end": 92, "ent_type": "MISC", "text": "Dutch"}, {"start": 116, "end": 129, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "PSV Eindhoven"}, {"start": 155, "end": 163, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "Volendam"}]}
{"id": "test-03407", "text": "Their other marksmen were Brazilian defender Vampeta and Belgian striker Luc Nilis, his 14th of the season.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 26, "end": 35, "ent_type": "MISC", "text": "Brazilian"}, {"start": 45, "end": 52, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Vampeta"}, {"start": 57, "end": 64, "ent_type": "MISC", "text": "Belgian"}, {"start": 73, "end": 82, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Luc Nilis"}]}
{"id": "test-03408", "text": "PSV, well on the way to their 14th league title, outgunned Volendam in every department of the game.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 3, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "PSV"}, {"start": 59, "end": 67, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "Volendam"}]}
{"id": "test-03409", "text": "They boast a nine-point lead over Feyenoord, who have two games in hand, and are 16 points clear of champions Ajax Amsterdam, who have played 18 matches compared to PSV's 19.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 34, "end": 43, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "Feyenoord"}, {"start": 110, "end": 124, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "Ajax Amsterdam"}, {"start": 165, "end": 168, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "PSV"}]}
{"id": "test-03410", "text": "Ajax face AZ Alkmaar away on Sunday and Feyenoord, eliminated from the UEFA Cup after losing 4-2 on aggregate to Tenerife on Tuesday, travel to De Graafschap Doetinchem.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 4, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "Ajax"}, {"start": 10, "end": 20, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "AZ Alkmaar"}, {"start": 40, "end": 49, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "Feyenoord"}, {"start": 71, "end": 79, "ent_type": "MISC", "text": "UEFA Cup"}, {"start": 113, "end": 121, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "Tenerife"}, {"start": 144, "end": 168, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "De Graafschap Doetinchem"}]}
{"id": "test-03411", "text": "The Doetinchem side, dubbed \"The Super Peasants \", are one of the surprise packages of the season.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 4, "end": 14, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "Doetinchem"}, {"start": 29, "end": 47, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "The Super Peasants"}]}
{"id": "test-03412", "text": "They are fourth in the table.", "gold_mentions": []}
